'''異戊醛'''，又名'''3-甲基丁醛'''，是一種化學式為[[C5H10O|C<sub>5</sub>H<sub>10</sub>O]]的[[有機化合物|有機化合物]]。它在常溫常壓下為無色液體<ref name=Dictionary>Lewis, R.J. Sr.; Hawley's Condensed Chemical Dictionary 15th Edition. John Wiley & Sons, Inc. New York, NY 2007., p. 719</ref>，應用於工業合成中<ref name=Ullmann>Kohlpaintner, C. Ullmann's Encyclopedia of Industrial Chemistry: Aldehydes, Aliphatic, Wiley-VCH, 2000, Pg. 9 {{DOI|10.1002/14356007.a01_321.pub3}}</ref>，是[[正戊醛|正戊醛]]的[[同分異構體|同分異構體]]。

==存在==
異戊醛存在於[[橙|橙]]、[[檸檬|檸檬]]、[[尤加利樹|尤加利樹]]等植物的精油中，亦存在於[[啤酒|啤酒]]、[[芝士|芝士]]等加工食品中。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Isovaleraldehyde|url=https://www.acs.org/content/acs/en/molecule-of-the-week/archive/i/isovaleraldehyde.html|language=en|date=February 11, 2019|access-date=2020-09-06|archive-date=2020-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200726052657/https://www.acs.org/content/acs/en/molecule-of-the-week/archive/i/isovaleraldehyde.html}}</ref>
==製備==
異戊醛可以由[[異戊醇|異戊醇]]以[[重鉻酸鈉|重鉻酸鈉]][[氧化|氧化]]而成。<ref name=ChemicalBook>{{Cite web|title=异戊醛|url=https://www.chemicalbook.com/ProductChemicalPropertiesCB0351221.htm|publisher=chemical book|language=中文}}</ref>同時，可借由還原[[異戊酸|異戊酸]]來製備異戊醇，再將它氧化成異戊醛。<ref>{{Cite web|title=食品添加剂异戊醛（3-甲基丁醛）的基本信息|url=http://db.foodmate.net/additive/read_additivexz.php?pid=54|language=中文|access-date=2020-09-06|archive-date=2013-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130623165409/http://db.foodmate.net/additive/read_additivexz.php?pid=54}}</ref>

異戊醛亦可透過[[異丁烯|異丁烯]]在[[催化劑|催化劑]]、[[氫氣|氫氣]]與[[一氧化碳|一氧化碳]]的存在下發生[[氫甲酰化反應|氫甲酰化反應]]而生成，化學式如下：
:CH<sub>3</sub>CH<sub>3</sub>CCH<sub>2</sub> + H<sub>2</sub> + CO → (CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>CHCH<sub>2</sub>CHO

在[[啤酒|啤酒]]中，[[亮氨酸|亮氨酸]]會跟[[還原酮|還原酮]]產生一系列的化學反應，生成異戊醛。<ref name=Beers>Bamforth, C.W. Encyclopedia of Food Sciences and Nutrition (Second Edition) | Chemistry of Brewing, 2003, Pg.  440-447</ref>
==反應==
異戊醛帶有[[醛|醛]]的官能團，故可以被[[重鉻酸鉀|重鉻酸鉀]]等[[氧化劑|氧化劑]][[氧化|氧化]]成爲[[羧酸|羧酸]]（[[異戊酸|異戊酸]]）<ref>{{Cite book|title=Oxidation Reactions|last=E. Cheng, J. Chow, Y.F. Chow, A. Kai ,S.L.Lee,W.H. Wong|first=HKDSE Chemistry A Modern View|publisher=|year=|isbn=|location=|pages=}}</ref>，亦可以被[[氫化鋁鋰|氫化鋁鋰]]、[[硼氫化鈉|硼氫化鈉]]等[[還原劑|還原劑]]還原做[[異戊醇|異戊醇]]<ref>{{Cite book|title=Typical reactions of aldehydes and ketones|last=E. Cheng, J. Chow, Y.F. Chow, A. Kai ,S.L.Lee,W.H. Wong|first=HKDSE Chemistry A Modern View|publisher=|year=|isbn=|location=|pages=}}</ref>。同時，異戊醛可以將[[多倫試劑|多倫試劑]]（銀氨錯合物）還原成[[銀|銀]]，產生[[銀鏡|銀鏡]]。<ref>Brown, William H. See all 2 images Studyguide for Introduction to Organic Chemistry. ISBN 9781118083383. <!-- https://pa01000125.schoolwires.net/cms/lib/PA01000125/Centricity/Domain/366/Chap12%20Carbonyl.pdf --></ref>
==用途==
===有機合成===
異戊醛是種化工原料，可以用來合成[[新握克丁|新握克丁]]<ref name=ChemicalBook />、[[布噻嗪|布噻嗪]]<ref name=Ullmann />等藥品。
===製造香精===
異戊醛帶有水果的香氣（於極度稀釋時呈蘋果味，濃度低於10 ppm時是桃子味）<ref>{{Cite web|title=异戊醛|url=http://www.chemmade.com/assistant/chemdic/casDetail-590-86-3.html|language=中文|publisher= 中国化工制造网}}</ref>，可用於配置各種水果味的[[香精|香精]]。<ref name=ChemicalBook />
===工業===
異戊醛可作爲橡膠的[[促進劑|促進劑]]。<ref>Nils Nilsson. Analysis of chemical substances in balloons, 2007.<!-- https://www2.mst.dk/Udgiv/publications/2007/978-87-7052-662-3/pdf/978-87-7052-664-7.pdf --></ref>
